### Hi.
Welcome to Zlek, the remastered throwback to the first version of [My Website](http://aleksmiljkovic.github.io/). This website has no purpose, just random stuff. If you enjoy my websites, feel free to donate (Once I have a donation center set  up) for a shout out or an addition to the website. Have Fun!
```
"They hate us, cause they anus"
```
